data.description: Magnificent opportunity to move in this Fall! The incredible Sparkle floor plan located on one of the largest homesites in Sky Ranch has features you will love, Open concept living with a Gas Log Fireplace, Office/Flex Space for your needs, can be playroom, craft room or formal dining. The gorgeous kitchen has room to gather and is open to the expansive great room. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel Whirlpool appliances, including gas range and beautiful painted cabinets and stunning granite counters, in one word, STUNNING! This spacious floorplan has space for a separate family area in the big loft on the second floor. Beautiful Master Bedroom with 5 piece Master Bath; includes walk in shower and soaking tub. From sledding to mountain biking, Sky Ranch has it all, including a 22-acre central park which offers lots of fun outdoor activities. Play your favorite sport on a grass field, enjoy the many miles of trails, for big and little kids alike, or create your own adventure at one of Painted Prairie's environmentally inspired playgrounds. Exploring Sky Ranch's unique streetscapes, with their expansive views, and the neo-traditional land plan of the community, is an adventure in and of itself. And, of course, other escapes await as well as you explore Colorado's many nearby ski resorts, open spaces, and parks. Just a few minutes from Denver International Airport (DIA), Sky Ranch is easy-to-get-to and accessible to all. Work downtown? It's an easy 24-minute commute via car--or take the rail! Looking to ski? The closest resort is only an hour-and-a-half away. Centered on a magnificent ridge, the community offers an array of breath taking views, set in a community focused on activity and engagement. Coming home should always feel this good! Don't miss out on this rare opportunity to live in Sky Ranch!
